## 4. Do the artists actually separate?

### Centroids in PC space

![](output/06_artist_centroids.png)

```{r}
cmp_res$centroids |> kable(digits = 2)
```

### Unsupervised k-means (k = 3)

If the artists really inhabit different regions of feature space,
unsupervised k-means clustering with k = 3 should approximately
recover the artist labels.

```{r}
cmp_res$cluster_tbl |>
  as.data.frame.matrix() |>
  kable(caption = "Rows: artist label.  Columns: k-means cluster.")
```

Cluster purity (highest-frequency artist within each cluster, divided
by all tracks): **`r sprintf("%.3f", cmp_res$purity)`**.

### MANOVA on PC1..PC5

```{r}
if (!is.null(cmp_res$manova)) print(cmp_res$manova)
```

## 5. What makes Zutomayo "Zutomayo"?

Cohen's *d* between Zutomayo and the pooled
{Yorushika, Mrs. Green Apple} group, on each consolidated feature.
Positive = larger in Zutomayo.

![](output/07_zutomayo_vs_rest.png)

Top features (full table in `output/zutomayo_vs_rest_features.csv`):

```{r}
cmp_res$feat_stats |>
  slice_head(n = 12) |>
  mutate(across(where(is.numeric), \(x) round(x, 3))) |>
  kable()
```

